msgid "Light Attenuation"
msgstr "灯光衰减"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:8
msgid "Lamp panel, falloff options highlighted."
msgstr "灯光面板，高亮显示衰减选项。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:10
msgid ""
"There are two main controls for light falloff for *Point* and *Spot* lamps:"
msgstr "对于 *点光源* 和 *聚光灯* 有两种主要的控制灯光衰减的方法如下："

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:12
msgid "The lamp *Falloff* type selector."
msgstr "灯光 *Falloff（衰减）* 类型选择器。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:13
msgid "And the *Sphere* checkbox."
msgstr "*Sphere（球体）* 按钮。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:17
msgid "Falloff Types"
msgstr "衰减类型"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:20
msgid "Lin/Quad Weighted"
msgstr "线性/平方（Lin/Quad）权重"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:24
msgid "Lamp panel with Lin/Quad Weighted Falloff options highlighted."
msgstr "高亮显示的线性/平方（Lin/Quad）权重衰减选项的灯光面板。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:27
msgid ""
"When this setting is chosen, two sliders are shown, *Linear* and *Quadratic*, "
"which control respectively the \"linearness\" and \"quadraticness\" of the "
"falloff curve."
msgstr ""
"选择此设置时，将显示Linear 和Quadratic这两个滑块, 分别控制衰减曲线的“线性"
"度”和“平方度”。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:31
msgid ""
"This lamp falloff type is in effect allowing the mixing of the two light "
"attenuation profiles (linear and quadratic attenuation types)."
msgstr "这种灯衰减类型实际上允许混合两种光衰减曲线（线性和平方衰减类型）。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:36
msgid "Linear"
msgstr "线性"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:38
msgid ""
"This slider input field can have a value between (0.0 to 1.0). A value of 1.0 "
"in the *Linear* field and 0.0 in the *Quadratic* field in effect means that the "
"light from this source is completely linear. This means that at the number of "
"Blender Units distance specified in the *Distance* field, this light source's "
"intensity will be half the value it was originally."
msgstr ""
"这意味着在* Distance *字段中指定的Blender Units距离的数量，此光源的强度将是其原"
"始值的一半。\n"
"这个滑块的值在0.0和1.0之间。*Linear* 字段中的值为1.0时，*Quadratic* 字段中的值为"
"0.0意味着灯光效果完全受Linear的影响。这意味着光源强度到Blender *Distance* 字段的"
"单位的距离值只有原始光源的一半。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:44
msgid ""
"When the *Quadratic* slider is set to 0.0, the formula for working out the "
"attenuation at a particular range for full linear attenuation is:"
msgstr "当 *平方* 滑块设置为0.0时，在特定范围内计算完全线性衰减的衰减公式为："

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:47
msgid ":math:`I = E × (D / (D + L × r))`"
msgstr ":math:`I = E × (D / (D + L × r))`"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:49
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:87
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:104
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:295
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:331
msgid "Where:"
msgstr "在这里："

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:51
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:89
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:106
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:297
msgid "*I* is the calculated Intensity of light."
msgstr "*i* 是光的计算强度。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:52
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:90
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:107
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:298
msgid "*E* is the current *Energy* slider setting."
msgstr "*E* 是当前的 *Energy* 滑块的值."

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:53
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:91
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:108
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:335
msgid "*D* is the current setting of the *Distance* field."
msgstr "*D* 是当前的 *distance* 字段的值。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:54
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:109
msgid "*L* is the current setting of the *Linear* slider."
msgstr "*L*  是当前的 *Linear* 滑块的值。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:55
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:93
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:111
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:302
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:336
msgid "*r* is the distance from the lamp where the light intensity gets measured."
msgstr "*r* 是指与测量光强度的灯之间的距离。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:59
msgid "Quadratic"
msgstr "平方"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:66
msgid "Lamp with Lin/Quad Weighted falloff default settings."
msgstr "带有线性/平方（Lin/Quad）权重衰减选项的灯光默认设置。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:68
msgid ""
"This slider input field can have a value between (0.0 to 1.0). A value of 1.0 "
"in the *Quadratic* field and 0.0 in the *Linear* field means that the light "
"from this source is completely quadratic."
msgstr ""
"这个滑块可以接受输入的值在 0.0 到 1.0之间.  *Quadratic* 字段的值为1.0和 "
"*Linear*  字段的值为0.0意味着从光源发出的是完全的平方衰减光."

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:72
msgid ""
"Quadratic attenuation type lighting is considered a more accurate "
"representation of how light attenuates (in the real world). In fact, fully "
"quadratic attenuation is selected by default. For *Lin/Quad Weighted* lamp "
"falloff see Fig. :ref:`fig-bi-light-lin-default`."
msgstr ""
"平方衰减类型灯光是被认为是对光如何衰减更准确的表述 (在真实的世界). 实际上,  默认"
"选择是完全平方衰减。对于 *Lin/Quad Weighted* 衰减见图 :ref:`fig-bi-light-lin-"
"default` 。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:76
msgid ""
"Here again, the light intensity is half when it reaches the *Distance* value "
"from the lamp. Comparing the quadratic falloff to the linear falloff, the "
"intensity decays much slower at distances lower than the set *Distance*, but it "
"attenuates much quicker after *Distance* is reached."
msgstr ""
"同样，当光达到灯的 *Distance（距离）* 值时，灯光强度变为一半。将平方衰减与线性衰"
"减进行比较，强度在低于设定 *距离* 的距离处衰减得更慢，但在达到 *距离* 后衰减得更"
"快。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:82
msgid ""
"When the *Linear* slider is set to 0.0, the formula for working out the "
"attenuation at a particular range for full quadratic attenuation is:"
msgstr "当 *Linear* 滑块设置为0.0时，在特定范围内计算完全平方衰减衰减的公式为："

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:85
msgid ":math:`I = E × (D^2 / (D^2 + Q × r^2))`"
msgstr ":math:`I = E × (D^2 / (D^2 + Q × r^2))`"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:92
#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:110
msgid "*Q* is the current setting of the *Quad* slider."
msgstr "*Q* 是 *Quad* 滑块的当前设置。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:97
msgid "Mixing \"Linear\" and \"Quad\""
msgstr "混合“线性”和“平方”"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:99
msgid ""
"If both the *Linear* and *Quad* slider fields have values greater than 0.0, "
"then the formula used to calculate the light attenuation profile changes to "
"this:"
msgstr ""
"如果 *Linear* 和 *Quad* 滑块字段的值都大于0.0，则用于计算光衰减曲线的公式将更改"
"为："

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:102
msgid ":math:`I = E × (D / (D + L × r)) × (D^2 / (D^2 + Q × r^2))`"
msgstr ":math:`I = E × (D / (D + L × r)) × (D^2 / (D^2 + Q × r^2))`"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:115
msgid "Zeroing both \"Linear\" and \"Quad\""
msgstr "“线性”和“平方”归零"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:117
msgid ""
"If both the *Linear* and *Quadratic* sliders have 0.0 as their values, the "
"light intensity will not attenuate with distance. This does not mean that the "
"light will not get darker, rather it will, but only because the energy the "
"light has is spread out over a wider and wider distance. The total amount of "
"energy in the spread-out light will remain the same, though. The light angle "
"also affects the amount of light you see. It is in fact the behavior of light "
"in the deep space vacuum."
msgstr ""
"如果 *Linear* 和 *Quadratic* 滑块的值均为0.0，则光强度不会随距离而衰减。这并不意"
"味着光线不会变暗，相反，它会变暗，这只是因为光线所产生的能量分布扩散在更宽更远的"
"距离上而已。但是，扩散光中的总能量将保持不变。灯光角度也会影响你看到的光量。它实"
"际上是光在深空真空中的行为。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:125
msgid ""
"If what you want is a light source that does not attenuate and gives the same "
"amount of light intensity to each area it hits, you need a light with "
"properties like the *Constant* lamp *Falloff* type."
msgstr ""
"如果你想要的是一个不衰减的光源，并且它所照射到的每个区域的光强度都相同，那么你需"
"要一个具有 *恒定* 灯 *衰减* 类型属性的光源。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/lighting/lights/attenuation.rst:129
msgid ""
"Also, when the *Linear* and *Quad* sliders are both 0.0 values, the *Distance* "
"field ceases to have any influence on the light attenuation, as shown by the "
"equation above."
msgstr ""
"此外，当 *Linear* 和 *Quad* 滑块均为0.0值时，*Distance* 字段不再对光衰减产生任何"
"影响，如上面的等式所示。"

